<C>__{skipper}
<D>__{las estrellas es lo unico, que un marinero verdadero se mesesita para encontrarse. verdade patron?}
<A>__{the cubans stare back, frowning, amazed as they motor away. the crew are stunned by what they have just witnessed. skipper turns and meets the eyes of admiration, humility and complete respect. he joins alice at the helm. they linger for a moment.}
