<C>__{older chuck }
<D>__{with staff and string he showed us how to build a sextant. as we rode the trades, he shared the ancient secrets of how to read the waves and follow stars. and some mornings later, bathed in the orange glow of a sunrise, panama rose from the sea like a phoenix.}
